Brain Rarely Accepts Incoherent Nonsense (BRAIN)
version 0.1d1

BRAIN is an artificial intelligence system, featuring natural language conversation 
ability and inference features.

The system is extensible and uses whatever scripting language(s) you are most familiar to 
implement additional behaviours.


STATUS

The project is actively being developed, however, it is only in a very developmental/
prototype state and is not operational as yet.


AUTHOR

BRAIN is the work of Joshua Hawcroft <http://joshhawcroft.org/>



